readme: # material-design-syntax theme A syntax theme for Atom based off the beautiful colors of Google's Material Design color palette. Recommended to use this syntax-theme with [material-ui](https://atom.io/themes/atom-material-ui). ![A screenshot of my theme, in Java](https://i.imgur.com/dzUuqWu.png)
